spanGrp.span: NHK speaks about different ceremonies and festivals in the Tabaq community.
generally good recording quality, but some parts are in a very low voice (especially the ones by KBK)
Panasonic Lumix DMC-GH2K (set to AVCHD(1080i), FSH), plus external stereo microphone (Rode Stereo VideoMic) & windshield
Zoom H4n (set to WAV, 44.1Hz/16bit) + Beyerdynamic M 58 microfone
